(18, 'playstation_4_500gb', 'Playstation 4 500GB', 'The PlayStation®4 system opens the door to an incredible journey through immersive new gaming worlds and a deeply connected gaming community. With an astounding launch lineup and over 180 games in development the PS4 system offers more top-tier blockbusters and inventive indie hits than any other next-gen console. Developer Inspired, Gamer Focus. PlayStation 4. Greatness Awaits!', '', '<p class="productbyline" font-size:="" helvetica="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em 60px; padding: 10px 10px 10px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 24px; font-family: ">\r\n	The Playstation 4 500GB Blast From the Past System Bundle includes: PlayStation 4 500GB System Black (Pre-Owned Refurbished), Assassin&#39;s Creed Unity (Pre-Owned), Destiny (Pre-Owned) and a 2nd DualShock 4 Wireless Controller (Pre-Owned).</p>\r\n<div class="longdescription productbyline" font-size:="" helvetica="" style="color: rgb(32, 32, 32); padding: 10px 0px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 60px; font-family: ">\r\n	<div class="extra_content">\r\n		<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px;">\r\n			The Playstation 4 500GB Blast From the Past System Bundle includes:</h3>\r\n		<div class="extra_content_bundleitem" style="margin: 14.5938px; clear: both;">\r\n			<img class="ae-img" src="http://www.gamestop.com/common/images/lbox/020384b2.jpg" style="border: 0px; width: 140.156px; margin: 14.0156px;" />\r\n			<div class="extra_content_bundleitem_text" style="width: 525.609px; float: right; padding-top: 14.0156px;">\r\n				<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px;">\r\n					PlayStation 4 500GB Console (Pre-Owned Refurbished)</h3>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					The PlayStation&reg;4 system opens the door to an incredible journey through immersive new gaming worlds and a deeply connected gaming community. With an astounding launch lineup and over 180 games in development the PS4 system offers more top-tier blockbusters and inventive indie hits than any other next-gen console. Developer Inspired, Gamer Focus. PlayStation 4. Greatness Awaits!</p>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 74px; list-style: outside;">\r\n					<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\r\n						PlayStation 4 500GB Console</li>\r\n					<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\r\n						DualShock 4 Wireless Controller</li>\r\n					<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\r\n						HDMI Cable</li>\r\n					<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\r\n						Power Cord</li>\r\n				</ul>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="extra_content_bundleitem" style="margin: 14.5938px; clear: both;">\r\n			<img class="ae-img" src="http://www.gamestop.com/common/images/lbox/803723b.jpg" style="border: 0px; width: 140.156px; margin: 14.0156px;" />\r\n			<div class="extra_content_bundleitem_text" style="width: 525.609px; float: right; padding-top: 14.0156px;">\r\n				<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px;">\r\n					DualShock 4 Wireless Controller (Pre-Owned)</h3>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					The DualShock&reg;4 Wireless Controller features familiar controls, and incorporates several innovative features to usher in a new era of interactive experiences. Its definitive analog sticks and trigger buttons have been improved for greater feel and sensitivity. A multi-touch, clickable touch pad expands gameplay possibilities, while the incorporated light bar in conjunction with the PlayStation&reg;Camera allows for easy player identification and screen adjustment when playing with friends in the same room.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="extra_content_bundleitem" style="margin: 14.5938px; clear: both;">\r\n			<img class="ae-img" src="http://www.gamestop.com/common/images/lbox/150062b.jpg" style="border: 0px; width: 140.156px; margin: 14.0156px;" />\r\n			<div class="extra_content_bundleitem_text" style="width: 525.609px; float: right; padding-top: 14.0156px;">\r\n				<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px;">\r\n					Assassin&#39;s Creed Unity (Pre-Owned)</h3>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					Paris, 1789 - The French Revolution turns a once-magnificent city into a place of terror and chaos. Its cobblestone streets run red with the blood of commoners who dared to rise up against the oppressive aristocracy. As the nation tears itself apart, a young man named Arno will embark on an extraordinary journey to expose the true powers behind the Revolution. His pursuit will throw him into the middle of a ruthless struggle for the fate of a nation, and transform him into a true Master Assassin.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="extra_content_bundleitem" style="margin: 14.5938px; clear: both;">\r\n			<img class="ae-img" src="http://www.gamestop.com/common/images/lbox/150017b.jpg" style="border: 0px; width: 140.156px; margin: 14.0156px;" />\r\n			<div class="extra_content_bundleitem_text" style="width: 525.609px; float: right; padding-top: 14.0156px;">\r\n				<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px;">\r\n					Destiny (Pre-Owned)</h3>\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					Everything changed with the arrival of the Traveler. It sparked a Golden Age when our civilization spanned our solar system, but it didn&#39;t last. Something hit us, knocked us down. The survivors built a city beneath the Traveler, and have begun to explore our old worlds, only to find them filled with deadly foes. You are a Guardian of the last safe city on Earth, able to wield incredible power. Defend the City. Defeat our enemies. Reclaim all that we have lost. Be brave.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '1', '2447f-15.jpg', '', '', '', '2', 24000, 5, '0', '', '', '', '2017-05-11 06:02:43'),
(19, 'mionix_-_zibal_60_mechanical_keyboard_-_black', 'Mionix - Zibal 60 Mechanical Keyboard - Black', 'In ancient Greek, Zibal means "river", symbolize how Zeus thunderbolt helped create the mysterious river Phaethon. Just as the mythical Zibal conceals mysteries unknown to man, the Zibal 60 Mechanical Keyboard contains new, surprising features around every turn. Fusing the classic keyboard components you love with the advanced gaming features you need to reach the next level, the Zibal 60 gives you an edge over the competition, helping you defeat your favorite games. ', '', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">In ancient Greek,&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Zibal</span><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;means &quot;river,&quot; symbolizing how Zeus&#39; thunderbolt helped create the mysterious river Phaethon. Just as the mythical&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Zibal</span><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;conceals mysteries unknown to man, the Zibal 60 Mechanical Keyboard contains new, surprising features around every turn. Fusing the classic keyboard components you love with the advanced gaming features you need to reach the next level, the&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Zibal 60</span><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;gives you an edge over the competition, helping you defeat your favorite games.&nbsp;</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" />\r\n	<br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">If you&#39;re serious about gaming or programming on your computer, the Zibal 60 Mechanical Keyboard helps you create the ideal setup, with simple connection options, like a two-way USB hub and audio/microphone port. The unique Black Cherry MX mechanical key switches make every keystroke feel natural, while the green-backlit illumination scheme ensures a clear view, day or night. Multiply your advantage with the six-key rollover feature, enacting up to six different keystrokes from only one key. You have the gaming skill. Now, unlock the technological mysteries you&#39;ve yet to explore with the Zibal 60 Mechanical Keyboard.</span></p>\r\n', '', '1', 'a709a-16.jpg', '', '', '', '4', 800, 0, '0', '', '', '', '2017-05-11 06:14:58');

