; word-break: normal; font-size: 32px; font-weight: normal; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n			Outdoor Full-Angle Anti-Sunlight</h2>\r\n		<div class="left-side" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 75px; outline: none; word-break: normal;">\r\n			<h3 style="margin: -15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 18px; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n				180 Degree</h3>\r\n			<p class="g5-anti-sunlight-desc" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);">\r\n				All day, Strongest sunlight (150,000 lux &asymp; 13,900 foot-candle)</p>\r\n			<p class="subtitle" style="outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 20px; float: none; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 5px !important; padding: 0px 30px 0px 0px !important; border: 0px solid !important; background: url(&quot;//cdn6.bigcommerce.com/r-678b8dcecd8097c9a0dc483a251b63f87782244e/themes/ClassicNext/images/icon_arrow_down.png&quot;) right center no-repeat !important;">\r\n				Sunrise - Noon - Sunset</p>\r\n			<p class="g5-anti-sunlight-data" style="margin: -10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 25px; outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);">\r\n				0&deg;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 25px; outline: none; word-break: normal;">-</span>90&deg;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 25px; outline: none; word-break: normal;">-</span>180&deg;</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="left-side" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 75px; outline: none; word-break: normal;">\r\n			<h3 style="margin: -15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 18px; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n				360 Degree</h3>\r\n			<p class="g5-anti-sunlight-desc" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);">\r\n				Display