(13, '13', 'AquaTimer Wi-Fi Connected Garden Hose System', '<p>\r\n	Automate the care for your yard and garden with the AquaTimer Wi-Fi connected Garden Hose System. Connecting directly to your home&rsquo;s Wi-Fi network, this handy device allows you to schedule, manage, and control your hoses with ease. The AquaTimer easily screws into place on the spigot. On the bottom are four spaces for your hoses which can all be individually controlled, allowing you to water up to four zones independently.</p>\r\n', '', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/z5uTPXevJd0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Automate the care for your yard and garden with the AquaTimer Wi-Fi connected&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/luminous-planter-100-recyclable-planter-for-your-garden/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Garden</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">&nbsp;Hose System. Connecting directly to your home&rsquo;s Wi-Fi network, this handy device allows you to schedule, manage, and control your hoses with ease. The AquaTimer easily screws into place on the spigot. On the bottom are four spaces for your hoses which can all be individually controlled, allowing you to water up to four zones independently. The device also provides you with one-touch manual watering at the press of a button right on the front. The AquaTimer connects to the app which is accessible on your computer, smartphone or tablet so you can have peace of mind knowing your garden is looked after no matter where you are.</span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/z5uTPXevJd0" width="560"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Automate the care for your yard and garden with the AquaTimer Wi-Fi connected&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/luminous-planter-100-recyclable-planter-for-your-garden/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Garden</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">&nbsp;Hose System. Connecting directly to your home&rsquo;s Wi-Fi network, this handy device allows you to schedule, manage, and control your hoses with ease. The AquaTimer easily screws into place on the spigot. On the bottom are four spaces for your hoses which can all be individually controlled, allowing you to water up to four zones independently. The device also provides you with one-touch manual watering at the press of a button right on the front. The AquaTimer connects to the app which is accessible on your computer, smartphone or tablet so you can have peace of mind knowing your garden is looked after no matter where you are.</span></p>\r\n', '1', 'e3a36-122.jpg', '940c6-121.jpg', 'd76e6-123.jpg', '', '6', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2017-02-25 11:33:00'),
(14, '14', 'Lenovo’s Windows Holographic VR Headset', '<p>\r\n	Get set to experience VR in a smaller and lighter form with the Lenovo&rsquo;s Windows Holographic VR Headset. This working prototype will work with Microsoft&rsquo;s Windows Holographic platform. The company made the headset pretty comfortable for regular use.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Get set to experience VR in a smaller and lighter form with the Lenovo&rsquo;s Windows Holographic VR Headset. This working prototype will work with&nbsp;Microsoft&rsquo;s Windows Holographic platform. The company made the headset pretty comfortable for regular use. The suspending lenses in front of the users&rsquo; eyes are very comfortable. This is also better than securing them in place with a strap. The high-resolution display has two 1440 x 1440 OLED panels. It will use&nbsp;six degrees-of-freedom tracking without using any external camera. Other than the Windows Store applications, the headset will also be compatible with some Hololens&nbsp;software. The two cameras in the front are what makes this headset one of a kind. Coming up on&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/category/ces-2017/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">CES 2017</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">, this VR headset is up for sale sometime later in the year between $300-$400.</span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Get set to experience VR in a smaller and lighter form with the Lenovo&rsquo;s Windows Holographic VR Headset. This working prototype will work with&nbsp;Microsoft&rsquo;s Windows Holographic platform. The company made the headset pretty comfortable for regular use. The suspending lenses in front of the users&rsquo; eyes are very comfortable. This is also better than securing them in place with a strap. The high-resolution display has two 1440 x 1440 OLED panels. It will use&nbsp;six degrees-of-freedom tracking without using any external camera. Other than the Windows Store applications, the headset will also be compatible with some Hololens&nbsp;software. The two cameras in the front are what makes this headset one of a kind. Coming up on&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/category/ces-2017/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">CES 2017</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">, this VR headset is up for sale sometime later in the year between $300-$400.</span></p>\r\n', '0', '57d99-1x1.jpg', '7fc8e-lenovo-windows-holographic-vr-headset-01.jpg', 'cde8e-lenovo-windows-holographic-vr-headset-02.jpg', '', '3', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2017-03-02 11:44:48'),
(15, 'samsung_powerbot_vr7000_robot_vacuum', 'Samsung Powerbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum', '<p>\r\n	Clean your floors with minimal effort with the Samsung POWERbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum. Coming in at 28% thinner than previous models, this device packs a lot of power. The VR7000 Robot Vacuum is able to generate up to 20 watts of suction power.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Clean your floors with minimal effort with the&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/h7-wireless-speaker/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);" target="_blank">Samsung</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">&nbsp;POWERbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum. Coming in at 28% thinner than previous models, this device packs a lot of power. The VR7000 Robot Vacuum is able to generate up to 20 watts of suction power. It also uses an Edge Clean Master feature that can pick up debris as close as .5&rdquo; from a wall. In addition to these features, the POWERbot VR7000 is intelligent for a smarter clean. It has Visionary Mapping Plus and FullView Sensor 2.0. This vacuum can actually remember the layout of the room to ensure a thorough clean. Finally, the Intelligent Power Control feature helps it complete high-quality cleanings. The VR7000 will automatically adjust to different floor types with no human intervention.</span></p>\r\n', '', '0', 'aac0e-samsung-powerbot-vr7000-robot-vacuum-02.jpg', '0c8ce-samsung-powerbot-vr7000-robot-vacuum-04.jpg', '', '', '6', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2017-05-11 07:14:08'),
(16, 'brilliant_control_smart_home_hub', 'Brilliant Control Smart Home Hub', '<p>\r\n	Your intelligent home is only just a tap away when you have the Brilliant Control Smart Home Hub. Replacing your light switch, this device gives you instant access to your smart home appliances.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>\r\n	<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="360" mozallowfullscreen="" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/202471725" webkitallowfullscreen="" width="640"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Your intelligent home is only just a tap away when you have the Brilliant Control Smart Home Hub. Replacing your light switch, this device gives you instant access to your smart home&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/category/home-media/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">appliances</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">. This includes your thermostat, speakers, lights, and more. In addition, Brilliant Control features Amazon Alexa. You can ask a question and instantly receive an answer. With multiple Brilliant Control units, you can even video chat throughout your home. Installation takes just minutes, and the connection to your devices is even faster. Because you can use voice commands as well as motion control, your favorite home settings are always within reach. As well as the convenience, this can help you save on your energy bills. With Brilliant Control, you&rsquo;re always in control of your home.</span></p>\r\n', '', '1', '0c643-131.jpg', '59444-133.jpg', 'b6070-132.jpg', '', '6', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2017-05-11 07:14:27'),
